Adds extended html5 and css3 language support to the existing language support in Notepad++ (5.9.8)
some html5 elements and mainly css3 properties are still in draft stage and might be not supported by browser layout engines
further browser vendor specific css properties are not included

Replace the langs.xml file in username/Roaming/Notepad++ or change the corresponding tags

